author: Discovery
description:
Pack your garlic, wooden stakes, and ancient spells as you come along with explorer Josh Gates to investigate evidence of the supernatural. From a vampire's corpse in Eastern Europe, to a missing mummy in the Incan Empire, discover what bone-chilling secretes Josh unburies.

Stream Full Episodes of Expedition Unknown:

About Expedition Unknown: 
Josh Gates investigates the truth behind the world's most iconic and captivating legends. Leaving no stone unturned, his adventures take him around the globe as he immerses himself in the core locales linked to each tale.

About MythBusters:
Two special effects experts with over 30 years of experience set out to methodically bust three urban legends in each episode. They test theories to prove or disprove what is real and what is truly urban myth.
